          TABLE OF CONTENTS
---------------------------------------------------------------------
I.     Requirements  

II.    Usage

I.        REQUIREMENTS
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Tested with jquery v1.9.1 but may work with earlier versions.

II.       USAGE
---------------------------------------------------------------------
  $( "#tags" ).masterblaster( {
    animate: true,
    onRemove: null, //tagName
    onAdd: null, //tagName
    onInvalid: null, //tagName, errorMessage
    triggerKeys: [ 9 ], //keycode when entered adds the tag (9 - <tab>)
    tagRules: {
      unique: true,
      minLength: 3
    }        
  } );

  $( "#tags" ).masterblaster( "push" );
  $( "#tags" ).masterblaster( "pop" );
  $( "#tags" ).masterblaster( "remove", "tag" );

SEE example.htm
